{"tid":1521072,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"張家輝係激戰講既一段說話好岩今日 大家入黎睇一睇","createTime":"2019-08-31T04:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T07:03:40.000Z","uid":30635,"like":84,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2bc8b7abc66fe16e9d27769727241eb257a031","tid":1521072,"uid":30635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"&quot;一個拳手，一定要建立自己的節奏，能夠令對方跌進你的節奏，這樣他就被迫跟你走。節奏，也就是步，晃，虛拳，一看到機會，重拳!能打出自己的組合就是屬於自己的節奏。能夠打出多變的組合，就是一個好拳手。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我地既搵到自己既節奏 <br />\n今日出去勇武就係比對手迫我地跟住佢地既節奏黎行<br />\n琴日好多人都吹831係endgame <br />\n但大家記住 101先係要玩大佢既大日子 今日唔係<br />\n今日要be water 去行街<br />\n大家記得 不被捕 不流血 不受傷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ea46c8bbc8f7738fc85a298793104a35991556","tid":1521072,"uid":30635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8648466a5851445eacc355b0d39b8b2dbf2bce76","tid":1521072,"uid":143321,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpbCtPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpbCtPU.jpg&h=375a68d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11025b4ab6277a93c683db407d6d08f734fd1483","tid":1521072,"uid":30635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:02:56.000Z","msg":"我地每一位都係拳手 每位都要打出自己既節奏 咁先有機會贏到<br />\n今日衝只係跟住人地既節奏黎打 只得死路一條<br />\n所以大家今日要諗清楚應該做d咩"},{"pid":"e729ed06a4d81763a712d48b63e7fbde2c5a68e0","tid":1521072,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">830 大濫捕 黑警被斬 完全將焦點轉移<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 我地今日出黎目的係<br />\n<br />\n因為5年前831中共就普選設下「提名委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我要真普選！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日港島見！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9df3fa1a75168072456b6865ea19f497804967ad","tid":1521072,"uid":30635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8648466a5851445eacc355b0d39b8b2dbf2bce76","tid":1521072,"uid":143321,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpbCtPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpbCtPU.jpg&h=375a68d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d5a09fed9f86291bfde155a25740c3bfef0423","tid":1521072,"uid":30635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e729ed06a4d81763a712d48b63e7fbde2c5a68e0","tid":1521072,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">830 大濫捕 黑警被斬 完全將焦點轉移<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 我地今日出黎目的係<br />\n<br />\n因為5年前831中共就普選設下「提名委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我要真普選！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日港島見！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"港島見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab38139fb652acbb1754c9